📁 Root Structure

mineo-app/
│
├── app/                    # ROUTES (Expo Router)
├── src/                    # ALL NON-ROUTE CODE
├── assets/                 # Images, fonts, icons
├── store/                  # Redux store
├── constants/              # App-wide constants
├── types/                  # Global TypeScript types
│
├── app.config.ts
├── tailwind.config.js
├── babel.config.js
├── tsconfig.json
└── package.json

📁 app/ — ROUTING ONLY (Expo Router)

app/
│
├── _layout.tsx             # Root layout (providers, auth guard)
├── index.tsx               # App entry (redirect logic)
│
├── (auth)/                 # AUTH FLOW (grouped)
│   ├── login.tsx
│   └── register.tsx
│
├── (tabs)/                 # MAIN APP (after login)
│   ├── _layout.tsx         # Bottom tabs layout
│   │
│   ├── home.tsx
│   ├── journal/
│   │   ├── index.tsx       # Journal list / today
│   │   └── [id].tsx        # Single journal page
│   │
│   ├── journey.tsx         # Journey map
│   │
│   ├── habits.tsx
│   ├── goals.tsx
│   └── profile.tsx

📁 src/ — REAL APP CODE

src/
│
├── components/             # Reusable UI components
│   ├── ui/                 # Buttons, Text, Card, Modal
│   ├── journal/
│   ├── habit/
│   ├── goal/
│   └── journey/
│
├── features/               # DOMAIN FEATURES (IMPORTANT)
│   ├── auth/
│   ├── user/
│   ├── journal/
│   ├── moment/
│   ├── habit/
│   └── goal/
│
├── services/               # API layer (backend calls)
│   ├── api.ts
│   ├── auth.service.ts
│   ├── journal.service.ts
│   ├── habit.service.ts
│   └── goal.service.ts
│
├── hooks/                  # Custom hooks
│   ├── useAuth.ts
│   ├── useJournal.ts
│   └── useAppDispatch.ts
│
├── lib/                    # App utilities
│   ├── http.ts             # Fetch wrapper
│   ├── storage.ts          # SecureStore / AsyncStorage
│   └── auth.ts             # Token helpers
│
├── styles/                 # Global styles (NativeWind)
│   └── global.css
│
└── providers/              # App-level providers
    ├── ReduxProvider.tsx
    └── AuthProvider.tsx

📁 features/ is the HEART of your frontend

features/journal/
├── journal.slice.ts        # Redux slice
├── journal.types.ts
├── journal.selectors.ts
└── journal.logic.ts        # Business logic

📁 store/ — REDUX TOOLKIT

store/
├── index.ts                # configureStore
├── rootReducer.ts
└── middleware.ts

📁 constants/

constants/
├── colors.ts
├── routes.ts
└── env.ts

📁 types/

types/
├── api.ts
├── user.ts
├── journal.ts
└── navigation.ts

🔥 RULES (NON-NEGOTIABLE)

❌ No business logic inside app/

❌ No API calls inside screens

❌ No Redux logic outside features/

✅ Screens only compose components + hooks

✅ One feature = one folder

This is how real products stay sane.